计主题色，提升视觉舒适度 . 新增水生动效，动画融入水生设计理念，风格真实灵动 . 新增世界时钟追光技术，基于太阳及月亮方位模拟真实投影效果 . 新增主屏幕世界时钟显示不同时区时钟信息 . 升级量子动画引擎至 4.0 版本，新增行为判断，可识别复杂手势，优化交互模式 . 优化 UI 层级，带来清晰有秩序的视觉体验 . 优化动效，模拟真实物理运动轨迹，效果自然连贯 . 优化卡片设计，分类整合信息，提高信息获取速度 . 优化字体，排版更协调，增加易读性 . 优化系统图标，采用最新色彩体系，更具高辨识度，提升整体质感 . 优化系统插画，融汇多元文化，丰富插画内容  【高效便捷】 . 新增智能会议助手，提升会议网络和速记体验，增加通知轻提醒 . 新增支持一键入会及智能整理会议纪要，提升办公效率 . 新增大文件夹，全新桌面文件夹使用体验，一步打开文件夹内应用，支持滑动翻页 . 新增智慧息屏，支持息屏状态下显示音乐、打车、外卖动态信息（支持部分应用） . 新增 NFC 高校校园卡，无卡也可畅行校园（支持部分高校） . 新增双击电源键快速展示健康码 . 新增媒体播放中心，优化控制中心操作体验 . 新增智能日程管理和冲突提醒，合理安排个人时间 . 新增支持日历一键导入钉钉日程，一键添加邮件日程 . 新增支持日程识别，可通过识屏功能识别当前界面日程并一键导入到日历 . 新增截屏编辑支持涂鸦，升级涂鸦画笔 . 新增支持桌面添加卡片，提供更多个性化信息展示，丰富桌面可玩性 . 新增支持相册选中图片转 Word、PPT 和 Excel 等文档 . 升级超级文本至 2.0 版本，多场景下扫描图片支持智能识别文字提取信息 . 升级超级录音至 2.0 版本，增强搜索能力，支持导出图文数据 . 优化小布建议卡片，多场景动态推荐应用及服务  【无缝互联】 . 升级跨屏互联至 2.0 版本，支持手机音频通话在 PC 端接听和挂断，两端自由切换 . 优化跨屏互联 PC 端手机应用多开能力，支持多任务处理，提升工作效率 . 优化手机投屏，支持内容自适应投屏布局，投屏与手机使用互不干扰  【个性化】 . 新增 Omoji 多样素材，支持设置联系人头像，创作更多个性化虚拟形象 . 新增时光息屏显示，提供更多息屏个性化风格设置 . 优化高光时刻，智能识别并推荐视频中的精彩照片，一键导出保存至相册 . 优化人像绘影息屏显示，支持多种笔刷及线条颜色  【安全隐私】 . 新增分享图片一键自动打码功能，识别并模糊处理聊天记录中个人信息，保护隐私安全 . 新增权限建议，智能推荐权限，提升用机安全 . 新增防恶意诱导安装应用功能，支持智能拦截恶意弹窗与广告 . 优化私密保险箱，采用先进 AES 全量文件加密方案，增强私密文件安全性 . 优化支付场景的安全保护，支付安全无忧  【健康关怀】 . 新增使用儿童空间浏览器时自动切换为儿童模式，守护儿童健康 . 新增儿童空间环境光检测，触发提醒 . 新增儿童空间自动开启护眼模式，保护儿童视力 . 新增家庭空间查看家人健康数据，全面守护关爱家人 . 新增家庭空间健康异常数据及跌倒检测提醒  【性能优化】 . 新增超级计算平台，全方面提升系统流畅性、稳定性、续航时长及应用使用体验 . 优化耳返开放性，共建耳返能力生态，便于三方应用接入  【游戏体验】 . 新增自研 VRS 技术，动态调整分辨率，增强性能并降低功耗，提升游戏体验 . 升级 HyperBoost GPA 稳帧技术至 4.0 版本，实现关键场景帧率稳定，平衡性能与功耗","googlePatchDate":"2022/10/05 00:00:00","type":"normal","versionFilename":"PFFM10domestic_11_C.35_2022102615170147.zip","backVersionLink":"https://gpw13.myoas.com/artifactory/after-sale-local/21series/21005_T/正式版本/RC2/PFFM10domestic_11_C.35_2022102615170147.zip","filePath":"/dfs/23/03/07/b7dcf00801444fc5a43a4b1cd0ce4c98.zip","fileName":"PFFM10domestic_11_C.35_2022102615170147.zip","md5":"ae713a372c19e4d050cd466b34602e67","colorOs":"","androidVersion":"Android 13","updateDescEnglish":"A system update is available. Your system will be upgraded to Android 13. A new design philosophy, Aquamorphic Design, is adopted for this update. Highlights include vibrant theme colors, optimized task management tools, enhanced security and privacy, new Always-On Display styles, and refined visual effects. &quot;【New Design】 . Adds Aquamorphic Design theme colors for enhanced visual comfort. . Applies the Aquamorphic Design philosophy to animations to make them natural and vivid. . Adds Shadow-Reflective Clock, with shadow simulating the orientation of the sun and moon. . Adds a Home screen world clock widget to show the time in different time zones. . Upgrades to Quantum Animation Engine 4.0, with a new behavior recognition feature, which recognizes complex gestures and provides optimized interactions. . Optimizes UI layers for clearer and neater visual experience. . Applies real-world physical motions to animations to make them look more natural and intuitive. . Optimizes the widget design to make information easier and quicker to find. . Optimizes fonts for better readability. . Optimizes system icons by using the latest color scheme to make the icons easier to recognize. . Enriches and optimizes illustrations for features by incorporating multicultural and inclusive elements.  【Efficiency】 . Adds Meeting Assistant to enhance the meeting connecting and note-taking experience and introduces an option to make notifications more subtle and less distracting. . Adds support for one-tap meeting joining and smart meeting minutes to improve work efficiency. . Adds large folders to the Home screen. You can now open an app in an enlarged folder with just one tap and turn pages in the folder with a swipe. . Adds a new type of Always-On Display that shows live information about music, ride-hailing, and food delivery. (Supports only some apps) . Adds NFC university card. You can now use your phone as your university card. (This feature is only available in some universities.) . Adds support to double tap the power button to show your health code . Adds media playback control, and optimizes the Quick Settings experience. . Adds smart event management and conflict reminders to help with your scheduling. . Adds support for one-tap calendar sync to DingTalk and one-tap sync of email events. . Adds support for event recognition. You can use screen recognition to recognize and sync the events on the current screen to Calendar with one tap. . Adds more markup tools for screenshot editing. . Adds support for adding widgets to the Home screen, making information display more personalized. . Adds support for conversion of images in Photos to .doc, .ppt, and .xlsx formats. . Upgrades to Text scanner 2.0, which can recognize text and extract information from scanned images in multiple scenarios. . Upgrades Recorder. Search capabilities are enhanced and exporting images and text is supported. . Optimizes Breeno Suggestions to make scenario-based suggestions for apps and services.  【Seamless interconnection】 . Upgrades to Multi-Screen Connect 2.0. You can answer or hang up calls on a connected PC and even switch a call between your phone and PC. . Optimizes Multi-Screen Connect. You can open multiple mobile apps on a connected PC for efficient multitasking. . Optimizes Screencast, with cast content automatically adapting to the target screen.  【Personalization】 . Adds more Omoji materials to cover more scenarios. Omoji now supports to set the contacts avatars, fully expressing yourself with more customized avatars. . Adds Insight Always-On Display, with more personalized Always-On Display settings available. . Optimizes the Highlights feature. The system recognizes and recommends the best moments in videos to you, and allows you to export and save them to the Photos app with one tap. . Optimizes Portrait Silhouette Always-On Display, with more drawing tools and line colors available.  【Security &amp; privacy】 . Adds an automatic pixelation feature for chat screenshots. The system can identify and automatically pixelate profile pictures and display names in a chat screenshot to protect your privacy. . Adds smart permission suggestions to improve security. . Adds a feature to prevent malicious attempts to lure users into installing apps, supporting smart blocking of malicious pop-ups and promotions. . Optimizes Private Safe. The Advanced Encryption Standard (AES) is used to encrypt all files for enhanced security of private files. . Optimizes payment security.  【Health &amp; Digital wellbeing】 . When in Kid Space, your browser app automatically switches to Kids mode to create a child-friendly space. . Adds ambient light reminders in Kid Space. . Adds Eye comfort in Kid Space to protect children's vision. . Adds family health data in O Family. You can check the data to understand your family members' health status. . Adds notifications when O Family detecting abnormal health data and human falling on the ground  【Performance optimization】 . Adds Dynamic Computing Engine to improve the system speed, stability, battery life, and app experience. . Optimizes the IEM ecosystem to include more apps.  【Gaming experience】 . Adds self-developed VRS technology, which dynamically adjusts the resolution to increase the performance while saving power so as to improve the gaming experience. . Upgrades to HyperBoost GPA 4.0 to stabilize the frame rate and balance the performance and power consumption in key scenarios. &quot;    ","companyName":null,"fileSize":23284055358,"softwareVersion":null,"projectNo":"21005","host":"https://dfs-serverauto-cn.allawnfs.com","nvFileInfo":[]}]},{"versionType":"enterprise","packageInfoDetail":[{"inSalesLink":"https://dfs-serverauto-cn.allawnfs.com/dfs/23/12/18/d57ec05f1a794f63b51c7dcbc074ac43.zip","outSalesLink":"https://dfs-serverauto-cn.allawnfs.com/dfs/23/12/18/d57ec05f1a794f63b51c7dcbc074ac43.zip","marketModel":"OPPO Find X5","updateDesc":"1、基于MP9进行发布 2、验证基本功能，验证订单需求，需求链接http://alm.adc.com/OPPO/%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E8%